tionally, an electrocardiogram and serum electrolyte levels should also be obtained prior to initiating osilodrostat therapy and periodically thereafter.', 'Metabolism', 'The manufacturer recommends reducing the dosage of osilodrostat by one-half during concomitant use of a potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitor.', NULL, NULL, 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic');
